### Önce servisleri başlat:
### OrderService:   dotnet run --urls=http://localhost:5001
### ProductService: dotnet run --urls=http://localhost:5002
### Gateway:        dotnet run --urls=http://localhost:5000

### Gateway üzerinden siparişlere eriş
### YARP bunu http://localhost:5001/api/orders'a yönlendirir
GET http://localhost:5000/gateway/orders
Accept: application/json

### Gateway üzerinden sipariş detayı
GET http://localhost:5000/gateway/orders/1
Accept: application/json

### Gateway üzerinden ürünlere eriş
### YARP bunu http://localhost:5002/api/products'a yönlendirir
GET http://localhost:5000/gateway/products
Accept: application/json

### Direkt OrderService'e eriş (gateway bypass)
GET http://localhost:5001/api/orders
Accept: application/json

### Direkt ProductService'e eriş (gateway bypass)
GET http://localhost:5002/api/products
Accept: application/json